snippet.textDisplay: After listening to this song, I became crazy about Mame Khan's voice. I liked this song a lot. I must have watched it hundreds of times and I told many of my friends to watch this song. Even today, everyone in my office watches this song. Mame Khan, there is a lot of magic in your voice. Even though I don't understand any Rajasthani language, this voice enchanted me. The music of the song is melodious. After listening to this song, I went crazy for some time and from that I became a huge fan of Mame Khan. All his songs are in my mobile, I listen to his songs whenever I get time. I watched all his interviews on YouTube and later I got in touch with him in person. He is an amazing person and a very simple and down to earth person. Thank you Mame Khan sir
